PLOT / BIVARIATE REGRESSION

This plot uses the dataset english. The bivariate regression involves the relation between the lenght of words in English language and the written to spoken ratio using the BCN corpus of written English and the CELEX corpus of oral English. The variables are LenthInWords and WrittentoSpokenFrequencyRatio.

The Bivariate regression shows an R-Square of 0.041. (I assume I have to use the SSE or something to turn the negative values into negative something is missing)
